		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Wondrous Item - Uncommon</em></p><p><strong>Action</strong> - 1 Creature (Unlimited) - 1/Dawn</p><ul><li><p>While you touch one stone, you can cast <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.h4mjOlvvmxCLjzeV]{Sending}</em> from it. The target must be the bearer of the other stone. If no creature bears the other stone, you know that fact immediately and the spell isn&#39;t cast.</p></li><li><p>Once either stone is used to cast <em>Sending</em>, neither stone can be used again until the next dawn.</p></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Utility</strong></p><ul><li><p>If one of the stones in a pair is destroyed, the remaining stone becomes nonmagical.</p></li></ul>",
